Seese Teakwood set Of 2 stools is made from high quality virgin plastic material with high durability. The product is delivered assembled. Unique Ratten wood finish/texture is suitable for adding aesthetic touch to your drawing room , office, garden, lawn , bathroom, etc. each stool Can carry upto 100 kgs weight and is comfortable, stylish and attractive.

Smooth, 360-degree turning radius,Adjustable height swivel, Wire-brushed effect and gray undertones, Pine veneers and solids, Faux rivets incorporate a rustic punch.

excerpt.rendered: Modern type of path stool that Made up of Plastic has Width x Height of 18 inch x 15 inch. Loading Capacity is 100 kg. The product is delivered assembled.
